# CI & Pre-Commit Discipline

- Pre-commit must mirror CI: black, ruff, flake8, mypy, pytest with coverage
- Default coverage threshold is enforced by CI; maintain ≥ configured value
- Default GH Actions matrix: ubuntu-latest, Python 3.10; full matrix only on release
- After triggering CI, wait ~2 minutes before checking status

